<TEXT>
<P>
 THE DISNEY POSTER: The Animated Film Classics from Mickey Mouse to Aladdin by 
Jim Fanning (Hyperion: $35.; 96 pp.) . This bright, colorful volume celebrates 
the artwork created to advertise the Disney shorts and features. As the 
illustrations were not done by the animators, it's interesting to observe the 
differences in the way the characters are drawn. The chapters on Mickey, Donald 
and Goofy reveal how the look of those popular icons changed over the decades. 
Fanning's cheerful, superficial survey will delight Disney fans and Disneyana 
collectors. Charles Solomon 
</P>
