<TEXT>
<P>
 We never thought pleasure in the 
</P>
<P>
 detached world 
</P>
<P>
 would be as much as a grain of salt or 
</P>
<P>
 sand. 
</P>
<P>
 When we were young, yesterday, 
</P>
<P>
