</P>
<P>
 we went straight from the movies to the 
</P>
<P>
 seashore 
</P>
<P>
 knowing art and life were separate, 
</P>
<P>
 friendly, 
</P>
<P>
 and if the streamwater wasn't fit to 
</P>
<P>
