<TEXT>
<P>
 * 1/2 Hammer, "The Funky Headhunter," Giant. Hammer the gangsta rapper.Sounds 
silly, doesn't it? About as silly as most of this album. Hammer has 
opportunistically shifted genres now that pop rap, which he rode to 
superstardom, is on the skids. The problem is that Hammer has zero feel for 
gangsta rap. The album is not a total disaster, thanks to some smashing beats 
and the unbelievably funky "Don't Stop" -- but it's close. 
</P>
<P>
 New albums are rated on a scale of one star (poor), two stars (fair), three 
stars (good) and four stars (excellent). DENNIS HUNT 
