Westchester area Thursday, Friday and Saturday, plus the same days the 
following week to collect household hazardous waste. It is a drive-through 
collection program and operates only by appointment. Call Monday through 
Friday, 9 a.m. to 3 p.m. (800) 98-TOXIC. 
