<HEADLINE>
<P>
OFFICER'S DEATH BRINGS BOTH SADNESS AND UNITY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * The tragic death of Christy Lynne Hamilton has affected the entire 
community. Once again the ugly face of crime has impacted us, the officers that 
serve the community.We have had another member of our ever-so-small family 
taken away. 
</P>
<P>
 Though our spirits and feelings may be somber with our loss, Christy's death 
has brought out the community in their ever-present thoughtfulness and caring 
for the men and women of the Los Angeles Police Department. 
</P>
<P>
 Cards, letters, flowers and phone calls from the public have helped to relieve 
the sadness and sense of loss that is hanging over our heads. We will continue 
in our efforts to rid our communities of criminals so that we can make Los 
Angeles a safe place to live, work and play. 
</P>
<P>
 RICK GIBBY 
</P>
