/ Antelope Valley line. Jan. 14: 845 Jan. 19: 6,357 Jan. 26: 20,833 Feb. 2: 
10,226 Feb. 9: 7,673 Feb. 16: 7,530 Note: On Jan. 24, the Santa Clarita line 
was extended to Antelope Valley; on Feb. 9, a third round-trip train was added. 
</P>
