strikeouts for Westlake (2-0) in a second-round game. 
</P>
<P>
 Simi Valley 3, West Torrance 2 -- Brian Kavanagh scored the game-winning run 
on a wild pitch with two outs in the sixth inning after a pair of West Torrance 
errors allowed him to get into scoring position in an El Segundo Tournament 
Second round game. 
</P>
<P>
 Bill Scheffels struck out 10 and scattered five hits. Jeff Michael and Kary 
