COMMUNITY NEWS: SOUTH: WATTS; SERVICE IS THEME OF SCHOLARSHIP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A commitment to community service is the theme behind Drew Economic 
Development Corp.'s newly established scholarship for students at King/Drew 
Medical Magnet High School. 
</P>
<P>
