 Witnesses said the robber was white, had a round face, blue eyes and wore 
wire-rimmed glasses. He appeared to be in his mid-40s, 6 foot 2 and weighing 
210 pounds, Mendez said. The robber had short blondish-red hair and wore a 
white T-shirt and white baseball cap, he said. 
